== Rival Apprentices ==

AI rivals fight with player-equivalent stats. Their level scales with yours:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Character !! Fighting Style !! Threat Level
|-
| Kamil || Balanced attacks || Medium
|-
| Olvan || Heavy physical || High (defense)
|-
| Esuna || Healing + attacks || Medium (heals self)
|-
| Wilme || Pure offense || Very High
|-
| Lux || Physical combo || High
|-
| Valsu || Defense + heals || Low (heals self)
|-
| Lejes || Magic spam || High (magic)
|}

'''Rival Level Formula (US):'''
```
Rival Level = (Player Level × 1.2) + Random(0-3)
```

'''Rival Level Formula (JP):'''
```
Rival Level = Player Level + Random(0-2)
```

This is why rivals feel much harder in the US version.

