== US vs JP Stat Differences ==

The US version has significantly higher enemy stats:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Stat !! JP Multiplier !! US Multiplier
|-
| HP || 1.0× || 1.5×
|-
| Power || 1.0× || 1.8×
|-
| Guard || 1.0× || 1.5×
|-
| EXP || 1.0× || 0.7×
|-
| Gold || 1.0× || 0.8×
|}

This results in a much more difficult game with slower progression.

